archimate:BusinessObject.name: SchedulingServiceAtomic
archimate:BusinessObject.documentation: A SchedulingServiceAtomic object models a SchedulingService as an independent (i.e., stand-alone) TrafficConditioningService. This is fundamentally different than the SchedulingServiceComposite object, which is used to model a SchedulingService as the combination of other existing SchedulingServices (as well as providing its own extensions).
